BFS¶

Expected result for BFS A TO M:
    Path: A E I M
    Expand: A B C D E F G H I (G) (H) J K L M

Expected result for BFS C TO L:
    Path: C G H L
    Expand: C A G B D E H K (D) F (H) I J L

result = g.uninform_search('BFS', 'A', 'M', expanded_criteria='alphabetical')
